| Branch?           | 9.0.x
| Description?      | Fixes category cover vs thumbnail conflict, renders both properly in front office. See more below
| Type?             | bug fix
| Category?         | CO
| BC breaks?        | yes
| Deprecations?     | no
| How to test?      | read below.
| UI Tests          | https://github.com/Hlavtox/ga.tests.ui.pr/actions/runs/10903585728 https://github.com/florine2623/testing_pr/actions/runs/11009547904 ✅ 
| Fixed issue or discussion?     | Fixes https://github.com/PrestaShop/PrestaShop/issues/30520
